    <item>
      <title>波兰发行 30 亿欧元债券，以满足借贷需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/poland-sells-3-billion-of-bonds-amid-rising-borrowing-needs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰重返国际债券市场，出售 30 亿欧元（33 亿美元）的七年期和 15 年期债券，以在借贷需求激增的情况下获得融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/poland-sells-3-billion-of-bonds-amid-rising-borrowing-needs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 18:10:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对昂贵手袋的需求降温导致 LVMH 销售额下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/lvmh-quarterly-sales-drop-as-demand-cools-for-costly-handbags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为奢侈品行业最大的参与者，路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 的时装和皮革制品销售额出现疫情以来首次下滑，原因是中国消费者的需求暴跌给该行业带来了重创，而中国消费者对高端消费的需求曾经似乎是无法满足的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/lvmh-quarterly-sales-drop-as-demand-cools-for-costly-handbags</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:49:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大大幅降息押注推动加元创 2017 年以来最差表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/loonie-s-worst-run-since-2017-fueled-by-big-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大消费者价格报告疲软，增强了人们对加拿大央行将在未来几周加快降低借贷成本的押注，导致加元遭遇七年多来最严重的下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/loonie-s-worst-run-since-2017-fueled-by-big-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 14:06:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币波动性创 7 月以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/bitcoin-tops-67-000-to-reach-highest-level-since-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币价格两个多月来首次突破 67,000 美元，但随着美国大选临近，数字资产领域波动性再次回归，比特币价格也迅速受到交易员的冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/bitcoin-tops-67-000-to-reach-highest-level-since-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 14:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
